g.text: The traitstable is the central data table within AusTraits, with columns linking to ancillary tables.
taxadetails on each taxon in austraits
methodsdata on dataset and trait methods
taxonomic_updatesdetails on taxonomic updates made to the dataset
excluded_datasame as the traitstable, with the addition of an errorcolumn, indicating why data are excluded.
